{"tid":1985373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當兒登仔笑泛民咁多年做唔到野時 有人做實事發現「意樂Itamomo」分店:未持有有效的食物業牌照","createTime":"2020-04-23T06:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T13:03:06.000Z","uid":158404,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"48d0747e0cba221e42ce083183b91efa7c1d5519","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"[size=5]各位連登仔女手足，唔好再笑泛民咁多年做唔到野喇<br />\n佢地做唔到野係事實，但我地又做咗幾多實事呢?<br />\n係呢度我要好好褒揚<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「專業清算師」及葵廣「潮食閣」</strong></span>呢兩個好好做實事嘅例子:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-【抗暴之戰】望還押手足有啖好食 葵廣黃店申懲教署私人膳食供應商<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200420/JBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FJBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6hSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=6235ec19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FJBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE%2F&h=37f3ec22\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200420/JBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE/</a><br />\n潮食閣FB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yummycornerhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyummycornerhk%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6hSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=fefec509\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yummycornerhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n-【拆定唔拆】TVBuddy命不久矣？ 網傳無綫冇交保留方案<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20191221/DMM7YQCREOM7I3CUHPFHJZYAOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20191221%2FDMM7YQCREOM7I3CUHPFHJZYAOI%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6hSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=5863a8bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20191221%2FDMM7YQCREOM7I3CUHPFHJZYAOI%2F&h=f2d66bb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20191221/DMM7YQCREOM7I3CUHPFHJZYAOI/</a><br />\n專業清算師FB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6hSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=4747bbff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/</a><br />\n<br />\n希望各手足要「深耕細作」，好多人話呢家係做最黑暗嘅時期，但各位手足應該盡量搵自己做到嘅野，去同中共港共死過。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n相信「蝴蝶效應」，你做一樣小事，<br />\n可以得到好大嘅效果。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人有個有相關專業嘅朋友，見到粉嶺闔府統請比人搞 (FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hopfutongching/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhopfutongching%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6hSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=511a50a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hopfutongching/</a>) : <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDiLeRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDiLeRU.jpg&h=73b68537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁的確，好似有啲兒登滲透5毛所講，犯規就要罰錢/改正架喇，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁無辦法喇，唯有<span style=\"color: red;\">以其人之道，還治其人之身</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢認為有藍店，例如「百分百餐廳」及「意樂Itamomo」分店，都有犯規之嫌，所以向政府部門作出投訴，<span style=\"color: red;\">慶幸我地仲有啲政府部門係會做野，有啲投訴已有回覆，其中有發現有「百分百餐廳」分店無遵守消防規定，甚至有「意樂Itamomo」分店原來連飲食牌都無!? </span><br />\n為咗保護所有相關人士，我將好多資料都隱藏咗:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5TLhQx9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5TLhQx9.jpg&h=eba98a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果真係，嚇人一跳!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，各位如果有咩睇唔過眼嘅店，記住跟我呢位朋友嘅方法，做啲實事喇。<br />\n非常簡單，如果政府部門人員肯做野，你就咁打個電話，Email打幾句指控，政府部門嘅人員已經會去跟進調查。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">暫時有嘅方向如下:<br />\n1. 環保署: 投訴通風系統噪音<br />\n2. 控煙辦<br />\n3. 消防署: 防火設施/條例<br />\n4. 海關: 商品說明條例/版權條例<br />\n5. 食環: 抗疫規定(沒有隔板並沒有隔開1.5米)、食店衛生<br />\n(食環呢班人，條2813線長期無人聽，要不斷打先有機會: 2868 0000，再應該係按1,1,0,2,2,2)<br />\n<br />\n如果有人有其他方向，請你留言教吓手足!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，請各位香港手足，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔好咁撚懶</span></span>，日日係度嗌好黑暗就算[/size=4]<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdd5117b3236207f97bd59e6afbd328f84cfad5","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:15:13.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"7557863506ec9fb34a647be9f2ed23829cdbd434","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"f4b0e85abd4ffd4c75a2a92eacf40057de4da8a7","tid":1985373,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"飲食牌都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a0251a0196d1a3fe201b1d8c05564c1968a7a2","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"6c2139075f4f00de771526521deccf9844b9d325","tid":1985373,"uid":164079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"推文回覆"},{"pid":"5c4263d5be4bf3d075844ca3eab5c40714a11085","tid":1985373,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"推做實事"},{"pid":"0676940404e943fb44f9bd2a32843b61860ff9db","tid":1985373,"uid":169529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"意八 桃園 百份百 味皇 全部同一集團"},{"pid":"bd14c1b11c3c3d852bc696cf5ebb934556c9063f","tid":1985373,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77aad3c4d982496e3941fed645fddb94a1cb2b0c","tid":1985373,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:29:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4400d8489230a0102b22e741e0b0f32f33d38cd","tid":1985373,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f8e563cc68d042edfa53ab09f997f07b1578b4dd","tid":1985373,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:37:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb6a99e107c099492e70d3cffdedd703dd74f92d","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"a49eb1d3bf1e3a1e9d715712fa2e3c2487c6b597","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"d65df140002a4b244c027e21ff0fdc063110a8ba","tid":1985373,"uid":76133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:45:17.000Z","msg":"意樂Itamomo 好撚難食. 呃錢份量少, 以後都唔幫襯.<br />\n杯即磨咖啡冇味, 好似飲緊屎水咁."},{"pid":"e01602c6f5a57d150c42772c710b2218ce440c06","tid":1985373,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"幾年前食過意樂，個豬骨拉麵湯底同出前一丁無分別"},{"pid":"cdfe95eaebb728ca26e7107cc639ace89251e356","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"0aba36b27bfe903dec2a5bba6bddee7a761de9f6","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"927c249d76d6c36fa42a7c134960eedb9be55015","tid":1985373,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T19:26:57.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"3207a46de241959777dc7527688f8561cf0da203","tid":1985373,"uid":92550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T19:31:02.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3560b8f74557f54612bb8cce029c0a30a105cfe6","tid":1985373,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"依個咁屌都無人推？"},{"pid":"d39ce39c9b2ec1372cd72ee5cbae48bc1fa36a3b","tid":1985373,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"8763507fbe5722db895b78dfbe37b660417fa736","tid":1985373,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"5f8426891e307bb2ad30ff29754eb7c72ab0cb27","tid":1985373,"uid":17623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"推呀！支持做實事呀！！！！"},{"pid":"5c2f67e66b8e0f273bf1ab53c175a4c8cec920e9","tid":1985373,"uid":129225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"正經post冇人推"}]}